{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"f4b540dd-c0bf-460f-9970-46c3b9bd7d0f","content":"The `.testsettings` format is **legacy** and ignored by MSTest v3+. You need to migrate to a `.runsettings` file. Here's what your file configures and how to migrate each piece:\n\n| `.testsettings` setting | `.runsettings` equivalent |\n|---|---|\n| `TestTimeout` (30 000 ms) | `<TestTimeout>30000</TestTimeout>` in `<MSTest>` |\n| Assembly resolution / deployment | `<DeploymentEnabled>true</DeploymentEnabled>` in `<MSTest>` |\n| Code Coverage data collector | `<DataCollector>` in `<DataCollectionRunSettings>` |\n\nLet me create the `.runsettings` file and wire it up:","toolRequests":[{"toolCallId":"toolu_vrtx_01H5BfkbLBTyJamjKEK5ASLN","name":"report_intent","arguments":{"intent":"Creating runsettings migration"},"type":"function"},{"toolCallId":"toolu_vrtx_01MmadpcMutpNVTZAEhLgf1Z","name":"create","arguments":{"path":"/tmp/sv-bfee171601f64b9f93d599e30c8d41a7/local.runsettings","file_text":"<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"utf-8\"?>\n<RunSettings>\n  <MSTest>\n    <DeploymentEnabled>true</DeploymentEnabled>\n    <TestTimeout>30000</TestTimeout>\n  </MSTest>\n  <DataCollectionRunSettings>\n    <DataCollectors>\n      <DataCollector friendlyName=\"Code Coverage\"\n                     uri=\"datacollector://Microsoft/CodeCoverage/2.0\"\n                     assemblyQualifiedName=\"Microsoft.VisualStudio.TraceCollector.SingleFileCodeCoverageDataCollector, Microsoft.VisualStudio.TraceCollector, Culture=neutral, PublicKeyToken=b03f5f7f11d50a3a\">\n        <Configuration>\n          <CodeCoverage />\n        </Configuration>\n      </DataCollector>\n    </DataCollectors>\n  </DataCollectionRunSettings>\n</RunSettings>\n"},"type":"function","intentionSummary":"create a new file at /tmp/sv-bfee171601f64b9f93d599e30c8d41a7/local.runsettings."},{"toolCallId":"toolu_vrtx_01QJiFoY4V9y434DFYaGNr1W","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/tmp/sv-bfee171601f64b9f93d599e30c8d41a7/TestProject